111&amp;pmid=19946589">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">9.</div><div id="r9" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Wang J, Fisher C, Thway K. Combined mesothelial cyst and lymphangioma of the small bowel: a distinct hybrid intra-abdominal cyst. <em>Int J Surg Pathol</em> 2014;22(6):547–551.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1177/1066896913509014">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24220997/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Combined+mesothelial+cyst+and+lymphangioma+of+the+small+bowel%3A+a+distinct+hybrid+intra-abdominal+cyst&amp;author=J+Wang&amp;author=C+Fisher&amp;author=K+Thway&amp;publication_year=2014&amp;journal=Int+J+Surg+Pathol&amp;pages=547-551&amp;doi=10.1177%2F1066896913509014&amp;pmid=24220997">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">10.</div><div id="r10" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">de la Plaza Llamas R, Ramia Ángel JM, García Amador C, López Marcano AJ. Chylous Mesenteric Cyst. <em>J Gastrointest Surg</em> 2018;22(5):921–922.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s11605-017-3606-8">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29043579/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Chylous+Mesenteric+Cyst&amp;author=R+de+la+Plaza+Llamas&amp;author=%C3%81ngel+JM+Ramia&amp;author=Amador+C+Garc%C3%ADa&amp;author=Marcano+AJ+L%C3%B3pez&amp;publication_year=2018&amp;journal=J+Gastrointest+Surg&amp;pages=921-922&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs11605-017-3606-8&amp;pmid=29043579">Google Scholar</a></div></